{"abstract": "While unisex personal care products proliferated a generation ago, the shampoo aisle remained a haven for unisex products, but that, too, is shifting.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/18/business/media/in-shampoo-ads-for-men-its-not-just-the-hair-its-what-it-does-for-you.html", "snippet": "While unisex personal care products proliferated a generation ago, the shampoo aisle remained a haven for unisex products, but that, too, is shifting.", "lead_paragraph": "WHILE unisex personal care products proliferated a generation ago, today the antiperspirant and soap aisles, for example, are dominated by products marketed to just men or women. The shampoo aisle remained a haven for unisex products, but that, too, is shifting, with Old Spice now introducing a hair care line, joining men\u2019s brands like Axe, which began selling hair products in 2009, and Dove Men+Care, which did so in 2013.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "3", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/18/business/ADCO/ADCO-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 913, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/02/18/business/ADCO/ADCO-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 913}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/18/business/ADCO/ADCO-jumbo.jpg", "height": 1024, "width": 673, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/18/business/ADCO/ADCO-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 2048, "width": 1346, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/18/business/ADCO/ADCO-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "wi